-- Gingrich to End Campaign Tomorrow, Spokesman Says
-- B y   J o n a t h a n   D .   S a l a n t
-- 2012-05-01T17:42:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-01/gingrich-to-end-campaign-tomorrow-spokesman-says.html
Former House Speaker Newt Gingrich
officially will end his Republican presidential campaign
tomorrow in Arlington, Virginia, spokesman R.C. Hammond said in
an e-mail.  Gingrich, who won just two primaries, will talk about
electing former Massachusetts Governor  Mitt Romney  to the White
House, Hammond said.  Hammond said April 25 that Gingrich would suspend his
campaign and endorse Romney.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jonathan D. Salant in Washington at 
 jsalant@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
